    done, else the line is appropriately justified. The method used is set by
    the variable ls$buffer-fill-mode(5)lm$buffer-fill-mode(5)le. Justify is usually used in conjunction
    with lswrap(2m)lmwrap(2m)le and lsindent(2m)lmindent(2m)le.


cESEE ALSO cA


