! 2mview
cEcENAME cEcA


    view - Read only


cESYNOPSIS cA


    cDview ModecA

    cDVcA - mode line letters.


cEDESCRIPTION cA


    cDviewcA mode sets the buffer to read-only, disabling the ability to alter the
