! 2medit
cEcENAME cEcA


    edit - Buffer has be changed


cESYNOPSIS cA


    cDedit ModecA

    cDecA - mode line letters.


cEDESCRIPTION cA


    cDeditcA mode indicated that the buffer has been edited. Many commands and
