    by default so cGspellutl.emfcA must be executed first using lsexecute-file(2)lmexecute-file(2)le.


cESEE ALSO cA


    lsadd-dictionary(2)lmadd-dictionary(2)le, lsedit-dictionary(3)lmedit-dictionary(3)le, lssave-dictionary(2)lmsave-dictionary(2)le,
