    tcl-lint - check a Tcl script file for  possible  problems  using the Python  package tclint/tclfmt
|%tcl-format-opts
    %tcl-format-opts - formatting command to be executed, default: "cCtcldmt --in-place %scA"
| %tcl-lint-opts 
    %tcl-lint-opts - linting command to be executed, default: "cCtclint %scA"
|%tclsh-com 
    %tclsh-com - name of the Tcl interpreter or PATH to it, default: "cCtclshcA"
