! 3 alias-path-setup
cEcENAME cEcA


    alias-path-setup - Define alternative path alias
$a


cESYNOPSIS cA


    cDalias-path-setupcA


cEDESCRIPTION cA


    cDalias-path-setupcA provides a dialog interface for declaring alternative
