cEcENAME cEcA


    !repeat, !until - Conditional loop (post testing)


cESYNOPSIS cA


    cD!repeatcA  
    ... loop body ...  
    cD!untilcA cCconditioncA  


cEDESCRIPTION cA


    The cD!repeatcA command operates in a similar fashion to ls!while(4)lm!while/!donele except
    the condition is tested at the end. Control finishes if the condition is
    met. As with the ls!while(4)lm!while(4)le there is no nesting of multiple cD!repeatcA
    statements.


cEEXAMPLE cA


    For example, the following macro segment fills to the fill column with
    spaces.

sB
          !repeat
              insert-string " "
          !until &equal $curcol $buffer-fill-col

